---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Terms & Conditions — Tony Ciencia" description="Terms and conditions of use for TonyCiencia.com and Tony Ciencia LLC services.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-inner">
      <h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>

      <h2>1. Acceptance</h2>
      <p>By accessing and using TonyCiencia.com you accept these terms in their entirety. If you disagree, you must stop using the site.</p>

      <h2>2. Service Description</h2>
      <p>TonyCiencia.com is an educational site about artificial intelligence, business automation and digital growth, operated by Tony Ciencia LLC (Albuquerque, NM, USA).</p>

      <h2>3. Permitted Use</h2>
      <p>You may access the content for personal, non-commercial use. Reproduction, distribution or modification of the content without prior written authorization from Tony Ciencia LLC is prohibited.</p>

      <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All site content (texts, images, logos, source code) is the property of Tony Ciencia LLC or its licensors and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.</p>

      <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Content is provided "as is" for educational purposes. Tony Ciencia LLC does not guarantee specific results and will not be liable for direct, indirect or consequential damages arising from use of the site or application of its content.</p>

      <h2>6. External Links</h2>
      <p>The site may include links to third-party sites. Tony Ciencia LLC does not control or take responsibility for the content of those sites.</p>

      <h2>7. Modifications</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site implies acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2>8. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of New Mexico, USA, without prejudice to rights afforded to users under the laws of their country of residence.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:contact@tonyciencia.com">contact@tonyciencia.com</a></p>

      <p class="legal-reviewed">Last reviewed: May 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: var(--spacing-16) var(--spacing-6); }
  .legal-inner { max-width: var(--content-width); margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-inner h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); }
  .legal-inner h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: 600; margin-top: var(--spacing-10); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-reviewed { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-top: var(--spacing-4); }
</style>
